# Memory write controller tiebreaker v1

You are deciding a single AGH Memory v2 candidate only when deterministic rules found a genuine ambiguity.

Return strict JSON:

```json
{"op":"add|update|delete|noop|reject","target_id":"","confidence":0.0,"reason":""}
